#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_call_to_action
msgid "2,000 parents<br/> brought their kid to our nursery."
msgstr "2.000 genitori<br/> portano i loro figli al nostro asilo."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        For every kid"
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Per ogni bambino"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Open-door policy"
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Politica porte aperte"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Our mission"
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        La nostra missione"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_banner
msgid "A little place <br/>of paradise"
msgstr "Un piccolo <br/>paradiso"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "About us"
msgstr "Chi siamo"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_image_text
msgid "Activities"
msgstr "Attività"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"All activities are planned to meet each child’s individual needs. This "
"approach will help your child to develop to the best of their ability."
msgstr ""
"Tutte le attività vengono pianificate per soddisfare i bisogni di ogni "
"bambino. Questo approccio li aiuterà a sviluppare le proprie abilità al "
"meglio."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_call_to_action
msgid "Contact us"
msgstr "Contattaci"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_kiddo.field_theme_utils__display_name
msgid "Display Name"
msgstr "Nome visualizzato"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_call_to_action
msgid "Entrust us with your children and go to work with peace of mind"
msgstr "Affidaci i tuoi figli e vai a lavorare in tutta tranquillità"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Events"
msgstr "Eventi"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_kiddo.field_theme_utils__id
msgid "ID"
msgstr "ID"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"Our aim is to make the early years of your child’s life as enjoyable, "
"rewarding and positive as possible."
msgstr ""
"Il nostro obiettivo è di rendere i primi anni di vita del tuo bambino "
"divertenti, pieni di soddisfazioni e il più possibile positivi."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_banner
msgid ""
"Our goal is to create a safe and nurturing environment for your child to "
"learn and grow. We believe that every child is unique and should be treated "
"as such."
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Our team"
msgstr "La nostra squadra"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_image_text
msgid "Our team is composed of experienced nursery nurses."
msgstr "Il nostro team è composto da puericultrici con esperienza."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Playground"
msgstr "Parco giochi"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_kiddo.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "Utilità tema"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_image_text
msgid ""
"They will propose to your children educational activities, playful, varied "
"and adapted to the stage of development."
msgstr ""
"Proporranno ai tuoi bambini attività educative divertenti, diversificate e "
"idonee per la fase di sviluppo."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Visit us"
msgstr "Vieni a farci visita"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"You are welcome to come and see the nursery and meet the team at any time "
"convenient to you."
msgstr ""
"Sei invitato a visitare l'asilo nido e a incontrare l'équipe in qualsiasi "
"momento ti sia più comodo."

